<rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News]]></title><link/> https://sputniknews.com/新闻<atom:link href="https://rsshub.app/sputniknews" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><description><![CDATA[news - Sputnik News - Made with love by RSSHub(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)]]></description><generator> RSSHub</generator><webmaster> i@diygod.me (DIY神)</webmaster><language> zh-cn</language><lastbuilddate> 2023 年 5 月 24 日星期三 02:21:29 GMT</lastbuilddate><ttl> 120 </ttl><item><title><![CDATA[Three Protesters Arrested After Cannes Center Left Without Gas, Power During Film Festival]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110550528" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105289/03/1052890314_0:0:1920:1253_1440x900_80_0_1_cc7ce624a213d6f01573b3b79a88eca9.jpg?source-sid=not_sputnik_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1052890313" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/three-protesters-arrested-after-cannes-center-left-without-gas-power-during-film-festival-1110550528.html?share-img=1052890313"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© 照片：Pixabay /</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">法国国旗</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="not_sputnik_photo" alt="French flag - Sputnik International, 1920, 24.05.2023" title="法国国旗" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105289/03/1052890314_0:87:1921:1167_1920x0_80_0_0_4a1b61fc80cdc07b01a67007a5043fe9.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105289/03/1052890314_0:87:1921:1167_640x0_80_0_0_1150b4fdc1289a4e3145b08ea72e93ea.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105289/03/1052890314_0:87:1921:1167_1280x0_80_0_0_3e10b292745c1cb53a61c1d95693a2d2.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/105289/03/1052890314_0:87:1921:1167_1920x0_80_0_0_4a1b61fc80cdc07b01a67007a5043fe9.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © 照片：Pixabay / </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据巴黎（人造卫星）网报道：法国媒体周二报道，在抗议有争议的养老金改革的抗议活动中，世界著名电影节正在举办的法国戛纳市中心已经没有汽油了。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 4月，隶属于法国劳工总联合会（CGT）的法国工会全国矿产与能源联合会威胁要让戛纳电影节陷入黑暗，以抗议改革。法国当局在 5 月初表示，由于可能发生示威，他们将加强节日的安全措施。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">据一家法国广播公司报道，巴黎时间下午 1 点（格林威治标准时间 11:00），该市围绕 Boulevard de la Croisette 的整个中心区域都没有天然气供应，而当时该地区的所有餐馆都坐满了客人。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"><strong>法国媒体透露，警方当场拘留了 GRDF 和 Enedis 能源公司的三名员工，他们负责切断戛纳的天然气和该市警察局的电力。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> CGT 已对这些行为负责。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">当天早些时候，媒体报道称，在 CGT 宣布抗议后，数百人聚集在戛纳火车站附近示威，反对改革。美国媒体援引工会的话说，它已经中断了该市的天然气供应，目标是戛纳影节宫和一些酒店和餐馆。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> 5 月 19 日，CGT 在戛纳卡尔顿酒店附近举行了一场示威活动，这是一家在电影节期间入住众多著名演员的豪华酒店。<strong>人们正在抗议改革，该改革将在 2030 年之前逐步将法国的退休年龄从 62 岁提高到 64 岁。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">第 76 届戛纳电影节将于 5 月 16 日至 27 日举行。</div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 24 May 2023 02:00:33 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230524/three-protesters-arrested-after-cannes-center-left-without-gas-power-during-film-festival-1110550528.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230524/three-protesters-arrested-after-cannes-center-left-without-gas-power-during-film-festival-1110550528.html<category>世界</category><category>欧洲</category><category>戛纳</category><category>法国</category><category>巴黎</category><category>总工会 (CGT)</category><category>反对</category><category>停电</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[Lesotho Willing to Extend Cooperation With Russia, Nothing Can Shake Ties - Envoy to US]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110550393" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/08/15/1099834501_0:0:1881:2821_1440x900_80_0_1_614bd91de180d862e61edf632faebe89.jpg?source-sid=rian_photo" data-photoview-image-id="1099834484" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/lesotho-willing-to-extend-cooperation-with-russia-nothing-can-shake-ties---envoy-to-us-1110550393.html?share-img=1099834484"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright">© Sputnik / Anton Denisov</span><span class="photoview__desc-text">俄罗斯联邦国旗于俄罗斯日在波克隆纳亚山庄严升起。</span> </div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="rian_photo" alt="The national flag of the Russian Federation was solemnly raised on the Day of Russia on Poklonnaya Hill. - Sputnik International, 1920, 24.05.2023" title="俄罗斯联邦国旗于俄罗斯日在波克隆纳亚山庄严升起。" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/08/15/1099834501_0:15:1881:1073_1920x0_80_0_0_7220f45987b15928e0facb1c2b2f704a.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/08/15/1099834501_0:15:1881:1073_640x0_80_0_0_b9b756a53a4ad420f5b416b8e6f13b04.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/08/15/1099834501_0:15:1881:1073_1280x0_80_0_0_26c37c125d0f855870e09022e1aeeb2b.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/08/15/1099834501_0:15:1881:1073_1920x0_80_0_0_7220f45987b15928e0facb1c2b2f704a.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> © Sputnik / 安东杰尼索夫</div>/ </div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">据华盛顿（人造卫星）网报道：莱索托王国驻美国大使图米桑·莫索托周二对人造卫星表示，莱索托愿意扩大与俄罗斯的合作，并认为双边关系不会受到任何影响。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">莫索托说：“我们与俄罗斯的关系一直很好。迄今为止，没有任何迹象表明有任何事情可以动摇我们与俄罗斯的友谊。” “我们与俄罗斯人民的友谊建立在坚实的基础之上。它源远流长。我同样相信，多年来我们一直是俄罗斯的好朋友。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">莫索托指出，俄罗斯和莱索托主要在教育领域开展合作。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> <strong>“但我们当然愿意扩大合作领域——当然是农业，当然还有贸易，”他说。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">大使周二进一步告诉人造卫星，他希望他的国家的代表将参加即将在圣彼得堡举行的俄罗斯 - 非洲峰会。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">当被问及莱索托王国代表团是否计划参加俄非首脑会议时，莫索托表示， <strong>“我愿意相信”。</strong></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “是的，我相信他们会的。我不知道安排有多远，计划是什么，但在所有条件相同的情况下，我想相信他们会参加，”他说。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>首届俄非峰会于 2019 年 10 月 23 日至 24 日在索契举行。</p><p>伴随而来的还有俄罗斯-非洲经济论坛。今年，根据此前的公告，第二次峰会和经济论坛均计划于7月26日至29日在圣彼得堡举行。</p></div></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 24 May 2023 01:32:28 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230524/lesotho-willing-to-extend-cooperation-with-russia-nothing-can-shake-ties---envoy-to-us-1110550393.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230524/lesotho-willing-to-extend-cooperation-with-russia-nothing-can-shake-ties---envoy-to-us-1110550393.html<category>非洲</category><category>莱索托</category><category>大使</category><category>俄罗斯</category><category>首脑</category><category>合作</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[South Carolina Governor Blasted for Saying He’d Like to Hunt Democrats With Dogs]]></title><description><![CDATA[<div class="article__header"><div class="article__announce"><div class="media" data-media-tipe="ar16x9"><div class="media__size"><div class="photoview__open" data-photoview-group="1110549901" data-photoview-src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/0c/02/1091212985_0:0:1920:1080_1440x900_80_0_1_9fc33a2c06786706c592622eb78e9140.jpg?source-sid=cc_0" data-photoview-image-id="1091212981" data-photoview-sharelink="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/south-carolina-governor-blasted-for-saying-hed-like-to-hunt-democrats-with-dogs-1110549901.html?share-img=1091212981"><noindex><div class="photoview__open-info"> <span class="photoview__copyright"><a href="https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/" title="CC0">CC0</a> / Pixabay /</span> <span class="photoview__desc-text">GOP，民主党</span></div></noindex><img media-type="ar16x9" data-source-sid="cc_0" alt="GOP, Democrats - Sputnik International, 1920, 24.05.2023" title="共和党、民主党" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/0c/02/1091212985_0:0:1920:1080_1920x0_80_0_0_881c464c1977d85194121c044422e22a.jpg" decoding="async" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/0c/02/1091212985_0:0:1920:1080_640x0_80_0_0_6424cc4229befc5f7b57d34a4ecc9100.jpg 640w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/0c/02/1091212985_0:0:1920:1080_1280x0_80_0_0_7e028f7d7f46a59c51a88a43e6ca18f8.jpg 1280w,https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e5/0c/02/1091212985_0:0:1920:1080_1920x0_80_0_0_881c464c1977d85194121c044422e22a.jpg 1920w" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div></div><div class="media__copyright " data-nosnippet=""><div class="media__copyright-item m-copyright"> <a href="https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/" title="CC0">CC0</a> / Pixabay / </div></div></div></div><div class="article__messengers"><div class="flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label"></span></div><div class="flex-align_center"></div><div class="article__telegram-news flex-align_center"><span class="article__google-news__label">订阅</span></div><div class="flex-align_center"><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/SputnikInt" title="国际的" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">国际的</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://telegram.me/sputniknewsindia" title="印度" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">印度</a></div><div class="article__telegram-button"><a href="https://t.me/sputnik_africa" title="非洲" class="" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">非洲</a></div></div></div><div class="article__author"><div class="article__author-item"><div class="article__author-wrapper"><div class="article__author-image"><img media-type="ar1x1" data-source-sid="" alt=" - Sputnik International" title="" src="https://cdn1.img.sputnikglobe.com/img/07e6/01/0b/1092187887_0:0:2048:2049_100x100_80_0_0_0c2cc4c84f89aff034cc55bb01fb6697.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div><div class="article__author-info"><div class="article__author-name">玛丽·曼利</div><div class="article__author-links"><a class="m-color-main" href="https://sputniknews.com/author_manley_mary/" title="所有材料">所有材料</a></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__announce-text">这一奇怪的声明是在周六的共和党大会期间发表的，并由一名记者发布在推特上。 </div></div><div class="article__body"><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">南卡罗来纳州州长亨利·麦克马斯特（右）最近因对政界同事发表了煽动性言论而陷入困境。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">据在活动期间<a href="https://twitter.com/JoeBReporter/status/1659950972020445184?s=20" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">发推文的</a>记者约瑟夫·布斯托斯 (Joseph Bustos) 称，麦克马斯特说：“我期待着民主党人如此稀少的那一天，我们必须用狗来猎杀他们。”</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">布斯托斯指出，这位共和党州长过去曾发表过这一评论，并且“在重复他最喜欢的共和党台词之一。” </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="social"><div class="ria-tweet"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">麦克马斯特重复他最喜欢的共和党台词之一：“我期待着民主人士如此稀有的那一天，我们必须用狗来猎杀他们。” <a href="https://t.co/O5HQcxowMi">https://t.co/O5HQcxowMi</a></p> - 约瑟夫·布斯托斯 🔥 (@JoeBReporter) <a href="https://twitter.com/JoeBReporter/status/1659950972020445184?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 5 月 20 日</a></blockquote></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">麦克马斯特的言论此后引发了强烈反对，一些人甚至暗示他的言论带有种族歧视色彩，可能会煽动暴力。南卡罗来纳州民主党人指出，州长所在的政党几乎全是白人，而该州的民主党人大多是黑人。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “南卡罗来纳州的大多数民主党选民是黑人，我们的州长大声说他迫不及待地想用狗来追捕我们，”南卡罗来纳州民主党主席克里斯塔尔西班牙在<a href="https://twitter.com/cspain1920/status/1660059052854919168?s=20" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">推特上写道</a>。 “听到一位了解我们历史的南方政府的消息，这绝对令人不寒而栗。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110549901" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/south-carolina-governor-blasted-for-saying-hed-like-to-hunt-democrats-with-dogs-1110549901.html?share-block=1110550263" data-title="“The majority of the Dem electorate in SC is Black and our governor is saying out loud he can’t wait to hunt us down with dogs,” Christale Spain, chair of the South Carolina Democratic Party, tweeted. “This is absolutely chilling to hear from a Southern Gov who knows our history.”"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">南卡罗来纳州民主党人现在要求他们的州长道歉并撤回评论。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">安德森县民主党主席克里斯·萨利 (Chris Salley) 要求州执法部门介入，如果州长不为他的评论道歉，萨利称其为“煽动政治暴力”，并在网上发起请愿以回应该声明。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “作为美国的一名黑人同性恋者，我一生中的大部分时间都不得不提防那些试图‘追捕我’的人，我知道南卡罗来纳州成千上万的人被迫有同感，”萨利<a href="https://www.facebook.com/andersondemocrats/posts/pfbid02de4CFy3opx7smyPZnVWaDMfbjnEhRKcYAFCC5W34t2KJAsFLk4mpEjHEApQwNdCLl" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener">说</a>. “这种言论助长了暴力极端分子的气焰，让政治话语寒心，需要结束。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110549901" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/south-carolina-governor-blasted-for-saying-hed-like-to-hunt-democrats-with-dogs-1110549901.html?share-block=1110550264" data-title="“As a Black, gay man in America, I’ve had to be on guard for people trying to ‘hunt me down’ most of my life and I know thousands of people across South Carolina are forced to feel the same,” Salley said. “This rhetoric emboldens violent extremists, chills political discourse, and needs to end.”"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text">麦克马斯特的一位发言人通过将评论视为“笑话”而为州长辩解。</div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="text"><div class="article__text"> “多年来，麦克马斯特州长一直在共和党大会上开这个玩笑，南卡罗来纳州人每天都明白这是个玩笑，”州长的通讯主管布兰登查罗查克 (Brandon Charochak) 告诉该报。 </div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="quote"><div class="article__quote"><div class="article__quote-text"> “如果南卡罗来纳州民主党的支持者再也无法忍受以他们为代价的轻松笑话，那么也许他们应该把精力集中在获胜而不是抱怨上。” </div><div class="article__quote-info"><div class="elem-info"><div class="elem-info__share"><div class="share" data-id="1110549901" data-url="https://sputnikglobe.com/20230524/south-carolina-governor-blasted-for-saying-hed-like-to-hunt-democrats-with-dogs-1110549901.html?share-block=1110550265" data-title="&quot;If South Carolina Democrat partisans can no longer bear light-hearted jokes made at their expense, then maybe they should focus their energy on winning and not whining.&quot;"></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="article__block" data-type="vrez"><div class="article__vrez"><div class="article__vrez-text"><p>美国媒体此前报道称，南卡罗来纳州州长在2018年的一次烧烤活动中将民主党人称为“狗”。 “我们的民主党朋友很像狗。一对一的，他们真的很好，但成群结队很危险，”他当时说。</p></div></div></div></div> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 24 May 2023 01:10:30 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://sputniknews.com/20230524/south-carolina-governor-blasted-for-saying-hed-like-to-hunt-democrats-with-dogs-1110549901.html</guid><link/> https://sputniknews.com/20230524/south-carolina-governor-blasted-for-saying-hed-like-to-hunt-democrats-with-dogs-1110549901.html<category>美洲</category><category>共和党人</category><category>共和党</category><category>民主党人</category><category>美国民主党</category><category>美国政治</category></item></channel></rss>